1. Nadam se da ću *ostati* u gradu za vikend. (I hope I will *stay* in the city for the weekend.)
2. Ako ne dođete na vreme, nećete *ostati* za večeru. (If you don't come on time, you won't *stay* for dinner.)
3. Kada sam pročitao knjigu, nisam mogao da *ostanem* ravnodušan. (When I read the book, I couldn't *remain* indifferent.)
4. Želeo bih da mi *ostaneš* prijatelj čak i ako se ne slažemo uvek. (I would like you to *remain* my friend even if we don't always agree.)
5. *Ostajemo* u kontaktu preko društvenih mreža. (We *stay* in touch through social media.)
6. Ako budeš ovako ljut, neću *ostati* sa tobom u istoj prostoriji. (If you're going to be this angry, I won't *remain* in the same room with you.)
7. Molim te da *ostaviš* ključeve na stolu kad odeš. (Please *leave* the keys on the table when you leave.)
8. Kada *ostanu* bez hrane, ljudi moraju da traže načine da prežive. (When they *run out* of food, people have to find ways to survive.)
9. Ako *ostaneš* do kraja filma, videćeš krajnje iznenađenje. (If you *stay* until the end of the movie, you will see a final surprise.)
10. Nemoj da me *ostavljaš* samog ovde, plašim se mraka. (Don't *leave* me alone here, I'm scared of the dark.)